name: test_NAF_2_1_0_unsuccessful_registration_due_to_invalid_email
description:
Test Case: NAF-2
    As a user I want to be able to sign to the app with email and password
    Scenario: Unsuccessful Registration due to Invalid Email
    
    Steps:
    1. Open the app
    2. Click on "Sign up" button
    3. Click on "Sign up with your email" button
    3. Enter invalid email: test@example.com
    4. Enter password: testpassword
    5. Click "Sign up" button
descriptionHtml:
Test Case: NAF-2
As a user I want to be able to sign to the app with email and password
Scenario: Unsuccessful Registration due to Invalid Email

Steps:
1. Open the app
2. Click on "Sign up" button
3. Click on "Sign up with your email" button
3. Enter invalid email: test@example.com
4. Enter password: testpassword
5. Click "Sign up" button
